Looking for members of Delta Company, 1/26, 3rd Mar. Div.(68-69)  Please be advised that Mike Agresti took his life. He is buried in Darian, Illinois at Claredon Hills Cemetery. I've met guys from Ollie North's unit including Jimmy Smith whos a cop in Chicago. They have a squared away reunion group that meets each year at a major city in the U.S. What the hell is wrong with 1/26, too much dinky dow?<br>
